                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181202-71-off398 t18181202-71-crimeloc401"></join>. On the 23d of November I was going towards Clifford's Inn, and felt a tug at my right hand pocket, turned round, and saw the prisoner<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181812020037"></xptr>with one end of my handkerchief in his hand, the other end was in my pocket. I collared him, and gave him in charge.</p>
